name: 2024 the 16th International Conference on Computer and Automation Engineering
content: Paper Publication: All full paper submissions will be peer reviewed and evaluated based on originality, technical merit and/or research content/depth, correctness, relevance to conference, contributions, and readability. Peer reviewed and presented papers will be published into ICCAE 2024 International Conference Proceedings, which will be archived in IEEE Xplore, and indexed by EI Compendex, Scopus, and other indexing services.
